nodes.text: Bill E. Martin (October 8, 1945 – January 27, 2016) was a voice actor who was credited with voicing "Bith Merchant, Gungan Guard, Fisherman, Lizard boy, and Naboo Soldier 2" in Star Wars Episode I: The Phantom Menace video game.
